  Translation choices to flag for native reviewer:
   - "Stimmung" used for "mood" everywhere (most common German wellbeing
     term). Alternatives: "Gemütszustand", "Befinden".
   - "Achtsamkeit" used for "mindfulness" (established German term).
     Alternative: keep English "Mindfulness" as loanword.
   - "Check-in" kept as English loanword. Alternative: "Eintrag".
   - "Begleiter" used for "Companion" (in compound "Elyria-Begleiter").
